stix:Indicator.indicator:Description:
This URL redirected systems visiting www.iraqiembassy.us. The domain resolved to 92.53.96.253 at the time of reporting. The observed activity for this URL was system profiling. The shortened URL http://goo.gl/QMC1jd redirects to this URL.

Pivoting off the URL shortener metrics for http://goo.gl/QMC1jd/ reveals the following referring domains:

conference.groningensolar.nl
www.russianembassy.org
www.iraqiembassy.us

Some of the function names in the profiling kit are below (available in full here: http://pastebin.ca/2844964). 
function md5cycle(x, k)
function md51(s)
function rhex(n)
function md5(s)

On 11 Dec 2014, access was attempted again via SOAP function calls, and an attempt to upload a web shell (base64 encoded) was detected. This IP address, along with those below, were seen attempting to execute SOAP functions on the server:

46.29.125.14   
198.203.28.43
